01:05:17.039 --> 01:05:19.226
You go out to dinner with him,
you talk about the script.

01:05:19.250 --> 01:05:22.128
And it took many,
many weeks until he finally said,

01:05:22.211 --> 01:05:24.505
"Yeah, I think that I can make
this work."

