01:07:39.139 --> 01:07:40.933
I had <i>Battleship Potemkin</i> in mind,

01:07:41.058 --> 01:07:43.143
the whole idea
of a baby carriage

01:07:43.227 --> 01:07:45.563
going down a staircase
in the midst of a shootout,

01:07:45.646 --> 01:07:47.690
and I just made it up
as I went along.

01:07:47.773 --> 01:07:49.775
♪♪

01:07:51.902 --> 01:07:54.864
[mouths]
My baby!

01:08:02.580 --> 01:08:05.291
[De Palma] The sequences
inspire the composer.

01:08:05.374 --> 01:08:07.835
You want to pare back
the sound effects

01:08:07.918 --> 01:08:11.714
and just use them to underline
certain things.

01:08:11.797 --> 01:08:14.341
Because you've got
97 tracks now,

01:08:14.425 --> 01:08:17.428
